{"tid":691971,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"比你揀, 要錢定健康?","createTime":"2018-06-06T08:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T23:43:55.000Z","uid":119385,"like":23,"dislike":71,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3055d5be64dd686d9fbbbc7aeef5605200000165","tid":691971,"uid":119385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:08:47.000Z","msg":"1)你係億萬富豪，要風得風要雨得雨，D靚女模特明星排住隊比你屌，平時出出入入都坐法拉利，但百病纏身，身患絕症，唔知幾時會死，吊得一日命得一日命。<br />\n<br />\n2)有健康體魂，但窮到連樓都無錢買既廢人。<br />\n<br />\n揀做有錢佬正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n健康窮撚負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa3e32202dd2d46c993e09f4a5632f5086ee2004","tid":691971,"uid":47268,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:09:52.000Z","msg":"你冇錢咁長命有撚用"},{"pid":"04e41ca92f7a44dab121d75958cff7b6cdef6662","tid":691971,"uid":119385,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fa3e32202dd2d46c993e09f4a5632f5086ee2004","tid":691971,"uid":47268,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:09:52.000Z","msg":"你冇錢咁長命有撚用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:12:39.000Z","msg":"但有錢得黎係百病纏身<br />\n最後會在極度痛苦中死去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49bc79d99fdef5c2274d9a365d092968e98f4856","tid":691971,"uid":105872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:14:31.000Z","msg":"2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n百病纏身既話屌女都無力屌了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ef30fab2969f6a13bdf5eddb932a884cf84b06","tid":691971,"uid":27766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:17:14.000Z","msg":"有錢人病都好快好返"},{"pid":"8567866b9813485a02eb723492dc7e021444818f","tid":691971,"uid":35524,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:20:33.000Z","msg":"真係咁有錢 百病纏身得去邊 <br />\n邊有咁多絕症 只有醫唔起既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif